Coty Inc. Appoints Camillo Pane as Executive Vice President, Category Development | Business Wire


























































Coty Inc. Appoints Camillo Pane as Executive Vice President, Category 
      Development






Brings Extensive Industry Experience in Senior Management and 
      Marketing Roles


Senior Executive Will Join the Global Beauty Company’s Executive 
      Committee










