NEW YORK--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Coty (NYSE:COTY) announced today the appointment of Camillo Pane as EVP 
      Category Development, effective July. Mr. Pane will join the Executive 
      Committee and report to Bart Becht, Chairman and Interim Chief Executive 
      Officer. Mr. Pane succeeds Renato Semerari, who will remain in his role 
