      all its businesses of Fragrances, Color Cosmetics, Skin Care and Body 
      Care.
    

      Mr. Pane was most recently Senior Vice President, Global Category 
      Officer Consumer Health at Reckitt Benckiser. In that role, he was 
      responsible for managing one of the largest and fastest growing 
