Mon, 09 Jul 2012 13:17:34 +0000
The Marketing Society
1160 at https://www.marketingsociety.com
https://www.marketingsociety.com/the-library/keys-reckitt-benckiser%E2%80%99s-success#comments


Judie Lannon, Annual Conference report – RB’s Camillo Pane
https://www.marketingsociety.com/the-library/judie-lannon-annual-conference-report-%E2%80%93-rb%E2%80%99s-camillo-pane
 <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>Reckitt Benckiser, which specialises in cleaning goods brands, has been a global success story of recent years; in his presentation, Pane explored how the company&rsquo;s culture has contributed to its success.</p>
<p>&bull; Speed of execution: a new category air freshener&nbsp; was launched in 8 months</p>
<p>&bull; Obsession with brands: never give up on marketing spend and exploit all communication channels</p>
<p>&bull; A truly global company: operations in different countries are likely to be run by non-nationals</p>
<p>&bull; Entrepreneurship: this includes allowing a recently-hired graduate with an idea for how to use Brasso, a polish, to (successfully) take this idea to market</p>
<p>&bull; Flat structure: disproportionate rewards for disproportionate achievement</p>
<p>&bull; Socially responsible: an admirable record on reducing carbon footprint</p>
<p>Judie Lannon, editor of The Marketing Society&rsquo;s quarterly journal, Market Leader, was reporting on our Annual Conference for Warc.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-feature-image field-type-image field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Feature Image:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.marketingsociety.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/thelibrary/Camilo%20Pane%20HS.JPG?itok=osfhysV_" width="154" height="220" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sub-header field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Sub Header:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Innovation through leadership and an entrepreneurial culture: Camillo Pane, general manager, Reckitt Benckiser, UK</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-rating field-type-fivestar field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Rating:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item">
 <div class="fivestar-default"><div class="fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5 clearfix"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="off">0</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div>
<div class="description"><div class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-average-count"><span class="empty">No votes yet</span></div></div>
</div>
